title: MULTIMILLIONAIRE PERV JEFFREY EPSTEIN NECK SNAPPED. What will autopsy reveal?
itunes:title: MULTIMILLIONAIRE PERV JEFFREY EPSTEIN NECK SNAPPED. What will autopsy reveal?
description:
Broken bones in millionaire Jeffrey Epstein's neck leads to much speculation that he did not commit suicide. Joining Nancy Grace today to look at the evidence is California Prosecutor Wendy Patrick, Forensics Expert Joseph Scott Morgan, Florida Medical Examiner Dr Tim Gallagher, Former FBI Special Agent Jeff Cortese and Radar Online Reporter Alexis Tereszcuk.
